married tomorrow.

17:45.265 --> 17:46.733
Magnolia's getting
married, too?
Shh!

17:46.733 --> 17:48.935
(whispers):
It is a secret...
All right.

17:48.935 --> 17:50.270
No, it's Lemon

17:50.270 --> 17:52.272
