Oh. (laughing)

17:52.272 --> 17:53.673
Yeah, sorry.
So anyway,

17:53.673 --> 17:56.776
so this veil is missing
a couple of, uh, of gems,

17:56.776 --> 17:58.278
you know, in the, uh...

17:58.278 --> 17:59.912
What do you call that?

17:59.912 --> 18:00.913
Tiara.
Yeah.

18:00.913 --> 18:03.082
Right, right.
Doc, uh...

18:03.082 --> 18:04.884
are you all right?

18:04.884 --> 18:06.419
Oh, yeah, yeah.

18:06.419 --> 18:08.621
Yeah. So we good for lunch?

18:08.621 --> 18:10.223
Lunch?
Launch.

18:10.223 --> 18:12.125
Good for launch?
Uh, yeah.

18:12.125 --> 18:13.626
Yeah, are we?
Yeah.

18:13.626 --> 18:15.528
Okay. Good-bye.

18:17.430 --> 18:19.466
You don't know anyone in this
town whose Internet service

18:19.466 --> 18:21.268
