by that pole that went down?

18:21.268 --> 18:22.735
I'm sorry, honey, but...

18:22.735 --> 18:24.804
sometimes it's good when
you can't get online,

18:24.804 --> 18:28.575
'cause it gives you a
chance to connect with a
real person for a change.

18:28.575 --> 18:31.043
Anybody have a satellite phone?!

18:31.043 --> 18:32.779
Sailors have satellite phones

18:32.779 --> 18:35.047
sometimes.

18:35.047 --> 18:36.516
No?

18:36.516 --> 18:37.784
'Kay.

18:37.784 --> 18:39.252
Go back to being

18:39.252 --> 18:41.454
no help at all.

18:41.454 --> 18:43.523
You, uh, you looking
for a hookup?

18:43.523 --> 18:46.159
Can you clarify what
you mean first?

18:46.159 --> 18:48.328
Internet. I've got
a dial-up connection.

18:48.328 --> 18:50.263
That's fantastic!
Let's go!

18:50.263 --> 18:53.500
(laughing):
Oh... I have waited so long
for that line to work.

18:53.500 --> 18:55.502
How far is your house?
Not far.
It's my mom's house,

18:55.502 --> 18:57.069
actually.
I live in the basement.

18:57.069 --> 18:58.805
The basement?
You do mean the basement

18:58.805 --> 19:00.139
and not a crawlspace, right?

19:00.139 --> 19:01.341
(laughs)

19:01.341 --> 19:04.244
No, seriously.
Wha...?

19:06.746 --> 19:08.748
(laughs)

19:08.748 --> 19:10.417
So, we got flowers?
We got champagne.
Yes.

19:10.417 --> 19:12.084
We got everything,
right? We can go
to Charleston now?

19:12.084 --> 19:14.387
Yes, unless you want to stop by
and get Oliver the organist.

19:14.387 --> 19:15.755
(laughs)
Very funny.

19:15.755 --> 19:17.257
(Lemon grunts)

19:17.257 --> 19:19.226
Magnolia, hold
that for me?

19:19.226 --> 19:20.760
Thanks.

19:20.760 --> 19:24.264
You know, you aren't supposed
to throw rice at weddings.

19:24.264 --> 19:26.065
It kills the birds.

19:26.065 --> 19:29.702
Well, aren't you a ray
of sunshine on a stormy day.
It's true.

19:29.702 --> 19:31.804
The birds eat it,
then they get so filled up

19:31.804 --> 19:33.440
on rice that
they don't want to eat

19:33.440 --> 19:34.774
anything else
that's good for them.

19:34.774 --> 19:36.175
And then they die.

19:36.175 --> 19:39.246
Yeah. I'm pretty sure
that's... not what happens.

19:39.246 --> 19:40.513
(laughs)

19:40.513 --> 19:43.983
(starter grinding,
engine stalling)

19:43.983 --> 19:45.985
(grinding continues)

19:45.985 --> 19:47.520
(engine stalling)

19:47.520 --> 19:49.722
