Is there a problem?

19:52.292 --> 19:54.327
Magnolia.
Mm-hmm?

19:54.327 --> 19:55.862
Did you, uh...

19:55.862 --> 19:58.298
happen to, while you
were waiting for us,

19:58.298 --> 20:02.168
have the radio and
the interior lights on

20:02.168 --> 20:04.771
while you had the
heat on full-blast?

20:04.771 --> 20:05.872
Maybe.

20:05.872 --> 20:08.408
It's freezing outside,
but it's okay

20:08.408 --> 20:10.877
after a while;
it just turned off by itself.

20:12.812 --> 20:14.614
Snow day.
Snow day.

20:14.614 --> 20:16.616
ERNIE:
 I don't get it.
 Are we gonna eat

