20:26.559 --> 20:28.728
All right?
Tonight we honor

20:28.728 --> 20:30.229
your 40 great
years of marriage.

20:30.229 --> 20:31.298
ERNIE: Well,
make up your mind.

20:31.298 --> 20:32.399
You want to honor 40 years

20:32.399 --> 20:33.633
or just the great ones?

20:33.633 --> 20:35.735
(laughing)

20:35.735 --> 20:37.169
DIDI:
Now,

20:37.169 --> 20:40.172
a stroll down
memory lane.

20:40.172 --> 20:41.374
Oh.

20:42.108 --> 20:44.243
(indistinct chatter)

20:46.579 --> 20:48.315
WADE:
Coming over.

20:48.315 --> 20:50.483
Uh, sit back

20:50.483 --> 20:51.984
and enjoy
a little show

20:51.984 --> 20:55.355
I like to call Carolyn
