23:21.768 --> 23:24.336
It lives to run, right?

23:24.336 --> 23:26.205
Sure.
Oh, yeah.

23:26.205 --> 23:29.008
Ladies, meet the boys.

23:29.008 --> 23:31.043
Boys, meet the ladies.

23:31.043 --> 23:32.645
(exhales)

23:32.645 --> 23:34.647
See why I called you
to come with me? Scary.

23:34.647 --> 23:36.148
I'm just glad he doesn't
have his mother

23:36.148 --> 23:37.617
