24:02.609 --> 24:03.610
ZoeHart2?
No.

24:03.610 --> 24:04.343
Favorite pet?

24:04.343 --> 24:05.444
Ooh, MrMittens.

24:05.444 --> 24:07.213
(ding)

24:07.213 --> 24:08.247
No.

24:08.247 --> 24:09.916
ZoeHart3? ZoeHart4?
No.

24:09.916 --> 24:11.751
Stop it... Wait, that's it.

24:11.751 --> 24:13.085
Okay.

24:13.085 --> 24:14.386
E-mail account.

24:14.386 --> 24:15.955
All right, come on.

